post_summaries.description: The image is a screenshot of an Instagram post by "fibwitv" featuring Carolina Kravacek (@caro.aracelik). She is standing in front of a backdrop with the words "MINU" visible. She is wearing a blue off-the-shoulder top and patterned blue pants. She is holding a red and white document with "30 Minutos" on it. There are two glasses and a white cone shaped lamp behind her. The post promotes her appearance on "En30Minutos" and highlights her project "Eco Mission," an app focused on environmental challenges.

The image shows a poster for "Gira Mujeres" (Women's Tour) by Coca-Cola. The poster highlights support for women's projects and features the Coca-Cola logo. The Instagram post itself mentions the user was a finalist in the Gira Mujeres program with Eco Mission.
The image shows a wedding photo. The bride and groom are smiling. The photographer is also visible in the corner of the image.
The image shows a woman (caro.aracelik) smiling in front of the Eiffel Tower in Paris, France.
The image shows two women standing on a bridge in Amsterdam, Netherlands. There are canals and buildings in the background.
The image shows a woman (caro.aracelik) standing in the Memorial to the Murdered Jews of Europe (Holocaust Memorial) in Berlin, Germany.
